OOC: Mosquitor? Just like, pretend you followed us or
something, if you want... :)

BIC: 

Tails lifted the slippery fish with her paws, trying
to get a hold on the wriggling body.
It flipped out and landed on the ground, flopping.
Tails wrinkled her nose delicately, and jumped on it,
trying to stop it from going any further.
But the fish flopped out of her reach...
The squirrel let out a sound that resembled a cross
between a growl and a squeak.
"MAXIMIZE!" She said suddenly, transforming.
Tails glanced at her "hand", and realized it was a
cannon of sorts that came out between her "fingers".
She shot it, aiming at the fish. The blast hit a tree
somewhere far, far away from the fish's direction, and
the shock caused Tails to fly backwards and hit the
ground.
She glared at the still-flopping fish with increasing
vengeance.
"Er, maybe I'm not as hungry as I thought.." She
called out to Goldeneye.
